  "tips": [
    "Strong house in the shape of a tower located on the top of a hill near the town of l´Esparra. The building is well preserved and defensive elements can be seen from its exterior.",
    "Magnificent Romanesque-style castle located in Turó del Vent, at 431 meters. You can enter the enclosure, walk through the roundabout and climb the tower from where you can see exceptional views of Les Guilleries and part of the Selva plain.",
    "Beautiful hermitage of Romanesque construction from the 12th century located very close to the castle of Farners. After a major expansion during the 18th century, the hermitage also has Baroque-style details."
